Some option for background image

Set the div (containing the bg image) to 100vh 

background-image: url("location");

background-size:cover; Scale the image to fit the width whilst maintaining aspect ratio.

background-position:center; if you need to center the image.

min-height:100vh; Ensure it covers the viewport height if required.

background-repeat:no-repeat  if required

Example
section.hero {
width:100%;
height:100vh;

background-image:url("images/bg_1.jpg");
background-size:cover;
background-repeat:no-repeat;
background-position:center;}



